OL,3,C'I wanted to help beat Hitler': 100-
OL,4,Cyear-old Windrush veteran
OL,6,FThe life of a 100-year-old Jamaican
OL,7,FSecond World War veteran who came to
OL,8,Fthe UK to join the Royal Air Force has
OL,9,Fbeen featured in a project to mark
OL,10,FWindrush Day.
OL,12,FWindrush Lincoln features the
OL,13,Ftestimonials of men and women from
OL,14,FLincolnshire who either travelled from
OL,15,Fthe Caribbean during the war or
OL,16,Fresponded to calls to help rebuild
OL,17,Fpost-war Britain.
OL,19,FOne of the stories is that of 100-year-
OL,20,Fold Ralph Ottey, who arrived in the UK
OL,21,Faged 19 to be an RAF volunteer.
