OL,3,C'I wanted to help beat Hitler': 100-
OL,4,Cyear-old Windrush veteran
OL,6,FMr Ottey said: "I was a great fan of
OL,7,FWinston Churchill, I knew all his
OL,8,Fspeeches. I knew what he was getting
OL,9,Fup to.
OL,11,F"I wanted to play my part in beating
OL,12,FHitler."
OL,14,FMr Ottey moved back to Jamaica after
OL,15,Fthe war but returned and settled in
OL,16,FBoston when the British Government
OL,17,Finvited people from the Caribbean to
OL,18,Fhelp fill post-war work shortages.
