OL,3,C'I wanted to help beat Hitler': 100-
OL,4,Cyear-old Windrush veteran
OL,6,FThe interview is thought to be one of
OL,7,Fthe poet's final official interviews
OL,8,Fand goes into great depth about his
OL,9,Fparents' journey from the Caribbean to
OL,10,FBritain in support of the recently
OL,11,Festablished NHS.
OL,13,FDavid Lambert, director of Cultural
OL,14,FSolutions UK, which is behind the
OL,15,Fproject, said: "They all have a story
OL,16,Fand we were curious about the
OL,17,Fconnections Lincolnshire had with the
OL,18,FCarribean.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
